1.text: Squeeze the amount of blue paint you will need for your project onto your palette.

2.text: Place a small amount of black paint next to the blue paint on your palette.
2.vid: /3/3e/Mix Colors to Make Dark Blue Step 2 Version 2.360p.mp4

3.text: Drag your brush through the edge of the puddle of black paint and pull a small amount of black  into the blue paint.
3.vid: /6/64/Mix Colors to Make Dark Blue Step 3 Version 2.360p.mp4

4.text: Mix the black into the blue paint a little at a time.
4.vid: /9/93/Mix Colors to Make Dark Blue Step 4 Version 2.360p.mp4

5.text: Add more black paint and mix as necessary until you reach your desired shade of blue.
5.vid: /4/44/Mix Colors to Make Dark Blue Step 5 Version 2.360p.mp4

7.text: Find the exact placement on the color wheel of the specific hue of blue paint you are beginning with.

8.text: Identify the shade of orange which is complimentary to your shade of blue.

9.text: Squeeze enough blue paint onto your palette to complete the coverage necessary with this shade of blue.
9.vid: /5/5a/Mix Colors to Make Dark Blue Step 9 Version 2.360p.mp4

10.text: Add a small amount of the orange paint next to the blue paint on your palette.
10.vid: /3/35/Mix Colors to Make Dark Blue Step 10 Version 2.360p.mp4

11.text: Drag your brush or palette knife tool through the edge of the orange paint and into the blue paint.
11.vid: /b/bf/Mix Colors to Make Dark Blue Step 11 Version 2.360p.mp4

12.text: Mix the orange paint into the blue.
12.vid: /b/be/Mix Colors to Make Dark Blue Step 12 Version 2.360p.mp4

13.text: Add more orange a little at a time until you reach the desired shade of blue.
13.vid: /f/f5/Mix Colors to Make Dark Blue Step 13 Version 2.360p.mp4

14.text: Pour some blue and purple paint on your palette.
14.vid: /6/6b/Mix Colors to Make Dark Blue Step 14 Version 2.360p.mp4

15.text: Mix a small amount of purple paint into the original blue.
15.vid: /2/29/Mix Colors to Make Dark Blue Step 15 Version 2.360p.mp4
